    <h2>Summary</h2>
    <p>Protonet is mainly developed to provide small and medium enterprises their own private, easy to administrate and secure cloud, but it can just as well be used for private uses, start-ups and freelancer as well as for project collaboration.</p>
    <p>The protonet node is a box arranging a local network, providing a fileserver with external access and establishing collaborative services with the push of a single button.</p>
