      <p>One of the main functions is the network storage. Every channel can have their own file depot that can be used just like (and even by) the well-known windows explorer or mac finder. Drop files, create folder, publish files in the channel and so on. Users subscribed to the individual channel can browse through and download the files. If you wish to give individual users or user groups specific rights for file access you can do so in the administration area that is clean and intuitive <a href="protonet_easy">simple</a>.</p>
