      <p>Users cannot only use the channels to exchange files; they can also inform about and discuss topics regarding each channel. Files can be published in the channel to be noticed, messages can be quoted, individuals can be addressed by name, links can be exchanged, video conferences can be held (soon), <a href="protonet_social">and so on</a>.</p>
